subproject.description: The project will  enhance capacities of the Ministry of Justice (MoJ) to develop, coordinate and implement justice sector reform measures. The project seeks to address urgent short-term capacity needs of MoJ at a time when it faces serious financial and human resources gaps. In addition to helping the Government pursue critical reform priorities, the intervention is designed to catalyze the implementation of justice sector reform. It will be coordinated and managed by the Ministry of Justice and will complement on-going work by other donors.
subproject.title: Justice Sector Reform

title: Support to Justice Sector Reform in Moldova
